---
import CTAButton from "../ui/CTAButton.astro";
import NavigationHint from "../ui/NavigationHint.astro";
---

<!-- Your Reserves Section -->
<section
  id="reserves"
  class="snap-none-mobile pt-24 pb-20 md:py-20 md:min-h-[100dvh] flex flex-col px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 border-t border-gray-800"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-16">
      Arrive rich
    </h2>
    <div
      class="prose prose-lg sm:prose-xl prose-invert max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12"
    >
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
        You've been accumulating knowledge and storing it away deep down your
        whole life — in your work, your relationships, your craft, your
        struggles. Wherever you've spent your best time and energy, you have
        accrued reserves of wisdom there.
      </p>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
        Not in every domain of life. But no one is impoverished across the
        board. Even where you're struggling practically, you have things to say
        that are worth saying and hearing — standing to speak importantly in a
        domain where you've known only discouragement.
      </p>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300">
        Most of these reserves of knowledge are unarticulated and even
        unacknowledged. Not because you lack something, but because articulation
        and acknowledgement need space, accompaniment, the right questions,
        someone on the other side to listen and to understand. What you know
        deep down is waiting to be uncovered and drawn out — traced back to its
        roots, tracked down in the outer reaches of all the other domains of
        your life.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Let's talk CTA -->
    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <CTAButton variant="secondary" />
    </div>

    <NavigationHint href="#solution" text="What we do" />
  </div>
</section>
